</em><em>旷野》</em> 、叙事悬疑小说<em>《肯塔基零号公路》</em>等等。每一个都可以成为一部不错的电影。</p>本文最初发表在 Engadget 上：https://www.engadget.com/cyberpunk-adventure-game-stray-will-be-adapted-as-an-animated-movie-174606306.html?src=rss]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/cyberpunk-adventure-game-stray-will-be-adapted-as-an-animated-movie-174606306.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> cc0192ab-2fff-4304-828a-17f49b5cdcb5</guid><dc:creator>劳伦斯·邦克</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>恩杰特</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder>恩杰特</dc:rightsholder><pubDate>Tue, 05 Sep 2023 17:46:06 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1693935672</ingested><modified> 2023-09-05T17:41:16+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[Consumer Discretionary]]></category><category><![CDATA[Movie Reviews]]></category><category><![CDATA[Movies]]></category><category><![CDATA[Media]]></category><category><![CDATA[Arts & Entertainment]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Lawrence Bonk]]></category><media:content height="1256" medium="image" url="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-09/bdbe1bf0-4c0e-11ee-aeb3-ce65d6b7a8ca" width="2000"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[ ]]></media:title></media:content><media:content height="1256" medium="image" url="https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-09/bdbe1bf0-4c0e-11ee-aeb3-ce65d6b7a8ca" width="2000"><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[2]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[BlueTwelve Studio ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[Screenshot fro