d-how-its-affecting-flights-12949666">问题发生时</a>，英国五分之一的出发航班和原定抵达该国的 27% 的航班被取消。</p>本文最初发表在 Engadget 上：https://www.engadget.com/united-airlines-has-grounded-all-flights-due-to-a-computer-issue-174007552.html?src=rss]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/united-airlines-has-grounded-all-flights-due-to-a-computer-issue-174007552.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> a7c83898-b781-4a0b-a022-64b2eae71964</guid><dc:creator>克里斯·霍尔特</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>恩杰特</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder>恩杰特</dc:rightsholder><pubDate>Tue, 05 Sep 2023 17:40:07 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1693936279</ingested><modified> 2023-09-05T17:51:21+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[Travel & Tourism]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Kris Holt]]></category><media:content height="4000" medium="image" url="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-08/e1576ef0-4c12-11ee-bf7d-a89f73e2a360" width="6000"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[ ]]></media:title></media:content><media:content height="4000" medium="image" url="https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-08/e1576ef0-4c12-11ee-bf7d-a89f73e2a360" width="6000"><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[2]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ASSOCIATED PRESS]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[A United Airlines plane is pushed from the gate at George Bush Intercontinental Airport Friday, Aug. 11, 2023, in Houston. (AP Photo/David J. Phillip)]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[United Airlines]]></media:title></media:content></item><item><title><![CDATA[The Android logo gets a new look and a 3D bugdroid]]></title><description type="html"><![CDATA[<p> <a data-i13n="cpos:1;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/tag/android-14/"><ins>Android 14</ins></a>即将到来。但在谷歌公开发布下一个大版本移动操作系统<a data-i13n="cpos:2;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/googles-pixel-8-event-is-set-for-october-4th-170334767.html"><ins>及其最新 Pixel 设备</ins></a>之前，该公司已经公布了更新的 Android 徽标。</p><p> Android 消费者品牌管理总监 Jason Fournier<a data-i13n="cpos:3;pos:1" href="https://blog.google/products/android/modern-look"><ins>在一篇博文中</ins></a>写道，该公司希望 bugdroid“看起来像 Android 本身一样充满活力”。通过彻底改变吉祥物的全身外观，我们希望 bugdroid 在数字和现实环境中看起来更容易保持一致。更新后的 bugdroid 和更新的徽标将于今年晚些时候开始出现在 Android 设备和其他地方。</p><span id="end-legacy-contents"></span><p>随着品牌重塑，<a data-i13n="cpos:4;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/tag/google/"><ins>谷歌</ins></a>还<a data-i13n="cpos:5;pos:1" href="https://blog.google/products/android/new-android-features-september-2023">透露了季度 Android 功能下降的细节</a>。最重要的功能是一个名为 Assistant At a Glance 的新小部件。这样做的目的是提供有用的信息，例如天气警报、活动提醒和旅行更新。该小部件使用人工智能来显示这些细节。</p><p> Android 即将推出一项听起来非常有用的辅助功能。这在 Lookout 上称为“图像问答”。您将能够使用语音命令或输入问题来了解有关<a data-i13n="cpos:6;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/tag/generative-ai/"><ins>AI 生成的</ins></a>视觉内容音频描述的更多详细信息。谷歌在设计该功能时考虑到了盲人和弱视人士。</p><p>您很快就可以将带有条形码和二维码的通行证（例如您的图书馆卡和健身卡）添加到<a data-i13n="cpos:7;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/tag/google-wallet/"><ins>Google 电子钱包</ins></a>中，从而无需随身携带这些通行证。您可以选择将 Fitbit/Google Fit 活动和睡眠数据添加到个人日常活动中，以帮助您跟踪您的健康目标。与此同时，谷歌重新设计了<a data-i13n="cpos:8;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/2019-09-30-google-car-crash-detection-pixel-us.html"><ins>个人安全应用程序</ins></a>，目标是让用户更轻松地分享自己的实时位置、记录周围环境以及拨打 911。</p><p>最后但并非最不重要的是 Android Auto 更新。 <a data-i13n="cpos:9;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/google-is-bringing-zoom-teams-and-webex-meetings-to-android-auto-200029169.html"><ins>Webex 和 Zoom 支持</ins></a>即将推出。您将能够通过音频加入电话会议并在汽车显示屏上查看会议日程。我们已经看到汽车制造商<a data-i13n="cpos:10;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/mercedes-benz-is-bringing-webex-meetings-to-the-new-e-class-sedans-050009834.html"><ins>将会议应用程序引入</ins></a>他们的信息娱乐系统，但 Android Auto 支持可能意味着无法逃避电话会议。</p><p>谷歌将逐步推出这些功能，将于今天开始在 Pixel 5、Pixel 5a 和 Pixel 4a 上提供。它们将在未来几周内登陆 Pixel 6 和 Pixel 7 系列手机以及 Pixel Fold。您可以期待<a data-i13n="cpos:11;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/googles-pixel-8-event-is-set-for-october-4th-170334767.html">Google 也将于下个月发布的最新一批 Pixel 设备</a>上提供所有这些功能。</p>本文最初发表在 Engadget 上：https://www.engadget.com/the-android-logo-gets-a-new-look-and-a-3d-bugdroid-170037292.html?src=rss]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/the-android-logo-gets-a-new-look-and-a-3d-bugdroid-170037292.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> 6cebbc9d-7527-440a-8f6c-94283874d96d</guid><dc:creator>克里斯·霍尔特</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>恩杰特</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder>恩杰特</dc:rightsholder><pubDate>Tue, 05 Sep 2023 17:00:37 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1693932141</ingested><modified> 2023-09-05T16:42:25+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[Software]]></category><category><![CDATA[Technology & Electronics]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Kris Holt]]></category><media:content height="847" medium="image" url="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-09/0ccc8ce0-4c0a-11ee-9dde-e5305ad2b934" width="1622"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[ ]]></media:title></media:content><media:content height="847" medium="image" url="https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-09/0ccc8ce0-4c0a-11ee-9dde-e5305ad2b934" width="1622"><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[2]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[Google]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[Refreshed Google Android logo alongside 3D renderings of the bugdroid mascot.]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[Refreshed Google Android logo alongside 3D renderings of the bugdroid mascot.]]></media:title></media:content></item><item><title><![CDATA[The best streaming devices you can buy in 2023]]></title><description type="html"><![CDATA[<p>如果您正在市场上购买新的流媒体设备，您很可能希望改善您的家庭影院体验。也许您一直依靠手机或平板电脑狂看您最喜欢的<a data-i13n="cpos:1;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/best-video-streaming-services-133000093.html">视频流服务</a>上的内容，或者您​​电视的内置操作系统可能不再能满足您的需求。目前，流媒体适配器（例如 Amazon Fire TV Stick Lite）和机顶盒（例如 Apple TV 4K）已经无处不在，但弄清楚它们之间的差异可能具有挑战性。此外，它们并不是唯一可以将您最新的 Netflix、Peacock 或<a data-i13n="cpos:2;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/best-live-tv-streaming-service-133000410.html">直播流媒体电视</a>节目呈现到屏幕上的小工具。让我们详细分析您今天拥有的所有选项，并为您挑选出您可以购买的最佳流媒体设备。</p><h2>谁需要流媒体设备？</h2><p>值得指出的是，如果您只使用几种流媒体服务（例如 Netflix 和 Amazon Prime Video），则可能不需要独立的流媒体设备。大多数现代电视都附带一系列基本应用程序，通常包括最流行的流媒体服务。一些电视和条形音箱在内置 Roku 或 Fire TV 操作系统上运行，无需单独的设备即可提供丰富的应用程序选择。</p><span id="end-legacy-contents"></span><p>但如果您的电视较旧，添加流媒体棒显然比购买新的智能电视便宜得多。此外，专用的流媒体设备通常可以访问更多的流媒体服务和应用程序，而内容通常会更直观地呈现。一些设备还提供更好的搜索功能，包括语音控制。掐线者尤其会受益于这种流媒体硬件，因为 Sling TV 和 Hulu Live 等直播电视服务并不总是在基本电视界面中可用。</p><h2>如何选择流媒体设备</h2><p>选择媒体流设备时要记住的最重要的事情是平台、价格和您家中已有的设备。目前，最流行的流媒体平台是 Roku、亚马逊的 Fire TV、Apple TV 和 Google TV（覆盖 Android TV 之上）。它们都提供类似的流媒体服务选择，主要区别在于用户界面。例如，Roku 具有基本的网格布局，而 Fire TV 和 Google TV 则强调个性化推荐。</p><p>流媒体设备的价格通常为 30 美元左右，最高可达 200 美元。棒或加密狗通常更便宜，而机顶盒往往更贵。选择流媒体盒而不是加密狗的主要原因是您是否需要以太网连接。某些型号还具有以太网端口和更快的无线连接等附加功能。 （例如，Roku 的机顶盒具有杜比视界，而其棒则没有。）机顶盒的另一个好处是它们比旧电视处理器更快，并且更容易随着时间的推移升级。</p><p>也存在一些功能差异。例如，Fire TV 使用 Alexa 进行语音命令，而 Google TV 使用 Google Assistant。事实上，当谈到来自亚马逊、谷歌和苹果的设备时，通常最好选择属于之前选择的生态系统的设备。因此，如果您已经是 iTunes 的忠实用户，Apple TV 会比 Fire TV 更有意义。当然，这并不是一条硬性规定：如果你更多地依赖流媒体服务而不是购买或租赁节目，那么生态系统问题就不那么重要了。我们将在本指南的后面部分详细介绍每个系统。</p><p>以下是一些有关最佳流媒体棒和其他经济实惠选项的建议。我们还提供了针对游戏玩家的机顶盒和设备的建议。</p><h2>最佳流媒体棒：Roku Streaming Stick 4K </h2><p><core-commerce id="52a5489094cc4d458672fbec17d415f5" data-type="product-list"></core-commerce></p><p> <a data-i13n="cpos:3;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAeD6Zl5kC5bCB1ZHeOCV6uvO4SfIINjXpS_BM6t8oUKw&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FRoku-Streaming-Device-Vision-Controls%2Fdp%2FB09BKCDXZC%2F">Roku Streaming Stick 4K</a>以及 Streaming Stick+ 等早期版本长期以来一直是 Engadget 的最爱，理由很充分：它在一个小巧且价格实惠的包中包含了许多功能。它具有简单的用户界面以及最广泛的流媒体电视选项。设置时您所需要做的就是将其插入电视的 HDMI 输入，并将电源线连接到电视的 USB 端口。之后，您可以通过电视界面和 Roku 遥控器完成其余的安装过程。</p><p>如前所述，Roku 有大量内容可供选择。据该公司称，您可以选择从超过 500,000 部电影和电视剧集中进行流式传输。另一个有用的功能是 Roku 的通用搜索功能，它可以在各种平台上查找节目，而无需优先考虑某个平台。相比之下，亚马逊的流媒体平台优先考虑来自其自己的 Prime 视频服务的搜索结果。</p><p> Roku Streaming Stick 4K 还支持 Apple AirPlay 2，因此非常适合那些想要从 Mac 或 iOS 设备进行流媒体播放的用户。此外，Roku Streaming Stick 4K 支持 4K、HDR 流媒体和杜比视界。</p><p>我们特别喜欢 Roku 的私人收听功能，该功能可让您使用耳机收听节目，如果您不想打扰其他家庭成员，该功能非常有用。您可以通过 Roku TV 应用程序执行此操作，该应用程序在 iOS 和 Android 上均可用。该应用程序还可以作为物理遥控器的替代品。这对于输入登录名和密码信息特别方便，使用智能手机键盘比使用遥控器进行搜索和啄食要容易得多。</p><p>除了遥控器之外，Roku Streaming Stick 4K 还可以响应语音命令，您可以用它来搜索您喜爱的节目、调整音量或启用隐藏式字幕。</p><p>如果您想要升级遥控器，请考虑升级到<a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;cpos:4;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAdVLMisE6xpyQLUjaqL0NkqVRDODa4_baPW6e5EU5-n-&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fgp%2Fproduct%2FB09BKCQYRN%2Fref%3Das_li_ss_tl" class="rapid-with-clickid" data-original-link="https://www.amazon.com/gp/product/B09BKCQYRN/ref=as_li_ss_tl?ie=UTF8&amp;linkCode=ll1&amp;tag=buyersguide2022-20&amp;language=en_US">Roku Streaming Stick 4K+</a> 。它具有 Streaming Stick 4K 的所有功能，但还配备了可充电的 Roku Voice Remote Pro。您可以通过说“嘿 Roku，我的遥控器在哪里？”来找到丢失的遥控器。它有一个内置的 3.5 毫米耳机插孔，因此您可以在没有应用程序的情况下使用私人聆听模式。不过，Roku Voice Remote Pro 比 Streaming Stick 4K 贵了近 20 美元，因此除非您确实需要那个精美的遥控器，否则我们建议您使用 Streaming Stick 4K。</p><h2>亚军：Chromecast 与 Google TV </h2><p><core-commerce id="5fc9ff0691f74f4393ad4278b9778586" data-type="product-list"></core-commerce></p><p>多年来，谷歌的 Chromecast 一直是一个没有遥控器的加密狗。它只是用于将手机或笔记本电脑上的节目流式传输到电视上。然而，更新后的<a data-i13n="cpos:5;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiI2NmVhNTY3YS1jOTg3LTRjMmUtYTJmZi0wMjkwNGVmZGU2ZWEiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYW1hem9uLmNvbS9ncC9wcm9kdWN0L0IwOEtSVjdTMjI_dGFnPWdkZ3QwYy1wLW8tZmwtMjAiLCJjb250ZW50VXVpZCI6ImI1NTdmMTBhLWE4MzctNDBiMy1hYWE2LTRhZTc3YzJmOTAzOSJ9&amp;signature=AQAAARwwjrJF1Znd_dFv5j8sxdkim6fB6HDDT-MrDxAZIMVt&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fgp%2Fproduct%2FB08KRV7S22">Chromecast with Google TV</a>则完全不同。它现在不仅拥有专用遥控器，而且还引入了全新的菜单界面和 Google Assistant 智能功能。虽然 Roku 可能是我们的整体选择，但 Google Chromecast 最适合那些喜欢更个性化界面和强大语音控制的人。</p><p>新Chromecast的亮点是Google TV，它实际上是Android TV的改进版本。主屏幕根据您的观看习惯进行个性化设置。有一个旋转木马，其中包含热门电视节目、精选精选节目以及“继续观看”和“Google 上的热门节目”等类别标题。我们特别欣赏“继续观看”行，因为它提供了一个快速的快捷方式来追赶您正在观看的节目（您猜对了）。</p><p>还有算法生成的推荐，例如“有关外星人的节目”或“有关谋杀的节目”。令人高兴的是，大多数建议的节目都来自您已经订阅的服务。如果您是 YouTube TV 订阅者，您会喜欢“直播电视”选项卡，它充当该服务的频道指南。不过，谷歌表示，该标签最终应该与 Sling 或 Hulu Live 等其他直播电视服务兼容。</p><p>我们还喜欢 Google TV 提供有关特定节目或电影的大量信息，例如烂番茄评级以及观看它的所有不同方式。您还可以直接从节目页面将其添加到观看列表中，无论它位于哪种电视流媒体服务上。不过，只能通过 Google Play 影视商店租借或购买该节目。</p><p>新的谷歌流媒体设备中我们最喜欢的功能之一是助理集成。您可以进行一般查询，例如询问五天的天气预报。最重要的是，诸如“查找比尔·默里主演的电影”和“向我展示真实的犯罪纪录片”等上下文查询都会出现高度相关的结果。您还可以完全通过语音命令控制电视，包括打开和关闭电视以及调节音量。</p><p> Chromecast with Google TV 支持 4K HDR 和杜比视界。但是，它不支持 Apple 的 AirPlay 2 协议，因此与 Mac 和 iOS 设备不太兼容。目前它也不支持 Apple TV+ 或 iTunes 视频。我们还应该注意到，与其他流媒体棒不同，最新的 Google Chromecast 无法通过电视的 USB 端口供电；您必须使用随附的 7.5 瓦电源适配器。</p><h2>最佳预算流媒体设备：Amazon Fire TV Stick Lite </h2><p><core-commerce id="44ff7eb83f7941d18bf1aad3c4710f0f" data-type="product-list"></core-commerce></p><p>如果价格是最重要的并且您不需要 4K， <a data-i13n="cpos:6;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAe-lj6bjW23mp7GrPWRpjS-jGHh21WrXxjYMQQ5wz6GC&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fgp%2Fproduct%2FB07YNLBS7R%2F">那么亚马逊的 Fire TV Stick Lite</a>是一个不错的选择。它的售价为 30 美元，是市场上最便宜的流媒体棒之一（也经常打折）。它支持带 HDR 的 FHD 流媒体，并且与其高端兄弟产品一样，配备了 Alexa 语音遥控器。</p><p>这被认为是“Lite”的原因之一是这个特殊的 Fire TV Stick 无法控制您的电视；您仍然需要使用电视遥控器来打开和关闭电视或调节其音量。这没什么大不了的，特别是如果它可以帮助你节省一些钱的话。相比之下，标准<a data-i13n="cpos:7;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiI2NmVhNTY3YS1jOTg3LTRjMmUtYTJmZi0wMjkwNGVmZGU2ZWEiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYW1hem9uLmNvbS9ncC9wcm9kdWN0L0IwOEMxVzVOODc_dGFnPWdkZ3QwYy1wLW8tZmwtMjAiLCJjb250ZW50VXVpZCI6ImI1NTdmMTBhLWE4MzctNDBiMy1hYWE2LTRhZTc3YzJmOTAzOSJ9&amp;signature=AQAAAXlG7-z5BgV4M3G48hv32hAtrHrWJO2qIlsCRVC8jPLO&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fgp%2Fproduct%2FB08C1W5N87">Fire TV Stick 的</a>零售价通常为 40 美元，而<a data-i13n="cpos:8;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAcO6yDSUwPJ7HnuRFgD0tsNrykiFvMziCbx34MLHpPFK&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fgp%2Fproduct%2FB08XVYZ1Y5%2F">Fire TV Stick 4K 的</a>零售价为 50 美元。</p><p>亚马逊的 Fire TV 支持几乎所有主要的流媒体服务，包括 Netflix、Hulu、HBO Max、YouTube、YouTube TV 和 Hulu 等。实时页面具有开箱即用的 Twitch。虽然您无法使用 Alexa 控制电视，但 Fire TV Stick Lite 可以让您使用 Alexa 搜索节目并询问一般问题，例如天气预报或您最喜欢的运动队的最新比分。</p><p>尽管价格低廉，Fire TV Stick Lite 仍然是一款不错的流媒体适配器。它配备了更新的 Fire TV 界面，添加了用户配置文件、带有节目推荐的新主菜单导航栏以及您最喜欢的流媒体应用程序的滚动列表等功能。</p><p>其布局不像 Google TV 那样直观，而且比 Roku 的更复杂，但仍然很容易理解。也就是说，该界面倾向于优先考虑 Amazon Prime Video 内容，并且广告比其他流媒体平台要多得多。它不是最好的流媒体设备，但如果您没有智能电视并且想以尽可能少的花费更新旧设备，那么它是最好的选择。</p><p>如果多花一点钱，您还可以升级到<a data-i13n="cpos:9;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAcO6yDSUwPJ7HnuRFgD0tsNrykiFvMziCbx34MLHpPFK&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fgp%2Fproduct%2FB08XVYZ1Y5%2F">Fire TV Stick 4K</a>或<a data-i13n="cpos:10;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAUJle3qAvQkby0wnKrXSACFfL8kUeoiWgo31lOOqFSCz&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fgp%2Fproduct%2FB08MQZXN1X%2F">Fire TV Stick 4K Max</a> 。两者都具有 4K、HDR、杜比视界和杜比全景声功能，但 Max 具有 WiFi 6 支持和更快的处理器。</p><h2>另一个预算选择：Roku Express </h2><p><core-commerce id="9f39ccd6b2244c5393802c6a08a418c4" data-type="product-list"></core-commerce></p><p> <a data-i13n="cpos:11;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAT77uX3qiyfFyOQNSkwIiiPDQwB1zciv-w3TbZUgdqZA&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fgp%2Fproduct%2FB07WVFCVJN%2F">Roku Express</a>具有与 Streaming Stick+ 相同的用户界面，但它安装在一个紧凑的机顶盒中。它不支持 4K 或 HDR，并且遥控器没有语音命令按钮。但如果您想要的只是一台功能强大的高清流媒体设备，那么 Express 就可以满足您的要求。不过，如果您坚持使用 4K，请考虑<a data-i13n="cpos:12;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAeIHd3VdyKEiRpyvPq4odcjjYpqzI4k4tIkniO3xsktn&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fgp%2Fproduct%2FB0916TKFF2%2F">Roku Express 4K+</a> ，其零售价为 40 美元。它与 Express 非常相似，不同之处在于它支持 4K、HDR 和 AirPlay，并且还配备了语音遥控器。这很可能值得花额外的钱。</p><h2>最佳机顶盒：Roku Ultra </h2><p><core-commerce id="9aea23acf00441d690fbf091f4372e93" data-type="product-list"></core-commerce></p><p> <a data-i13n="cpos:13;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAeCv9brqsdhoUyBXU_l4mWwo_C8Y2ojfUeZ3clMDTcJr&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fgp%2Fproduct%2FB09T4VZDYV%2F">Roku Ultra</a>具有与 Streaming Stick+ 相同的功能，甚至更多。有多种内容选择、简单的用户界面，并支持 4K HDR 流、AirPlay2 和语音命令。除此之外，Ultra 还增加了杜比视界支持以及 HDR 10+、USB 连接、用于外部媒体的 microSD 插槽和以太网连接。</p><p>与 Streaming Stick 4K+ 一样，Ultra 也配备了 Roku 的 Voice Remote Pro。遥控器还具有几个可编程快捷键，您可以将它们映射到特定命令，例如“启动 YouTube”或“播放古典音乐”。最重要的是，Ultra 具有远程取景器，以防您在沙发垫之间丢失它。 Ultra 绝对是市场上功能最强大的 Roku 设备，但您必须为此支付更多费用。</p><h2>最佳付费流媒体：Apple TV 4K </h2><p><core-commerce id="8e5c9a66a2214a31ba1f277904c55b97" data-type="product-list"></core-commerce></p><p>对于那些想要稍高端的选择并拥有大量苹果设备的人来说， <a data-i13n="cpos:14;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAeAhsSANR6AHEV91TGJBQ7fd1oLenitJA37vaFM2_rDH&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fgp%2Fproduct%2FB0BJLDVJTC%2F">Apple TV 4K</a>可能值得一掷千金。它可以以 4K HDR 和杜比视界进行流式传输，此外还支持 AirPlay 2，以便从 Mac 和 iOS 设备进行流式传输。 tvOS 平台拥有吸引人、简洁的用户界面，而且易于使用。还有“一个主屏幕”功能，可让您在多台 Apple TV 上同步应用程序及其布局，并且您可以使用 Siri 搜索您喜爱的节目。自从苹果改进了包装盒中附带的 Siri 遥控器以来，在应用程序之间导航、滚动内容以及快速找到您要查找的内容变得更加容易。</p><p>正如您所料，Apple TV 也是唯一一款与整个 Apple 生态系统兼容的机顶盒。这意味着您可以使用 Apple TV 从 iTunes 购买和租借电影、访问音乐和播客、从 Apple Arcade 玩游戏以及运行 Fitness+（Apple 的健身课程系列）等应用程序。</p><p> iPhone 用户尤其可能会从拥有 Apple TV 中受益。您可以在设置过程中将手机放在盒子上，以传输所有设置并直接通过远程应用程序输入密码，该应用程序本身可以通过 iOS 的控制中心轻松访问。</p><h2>最适合游戏玩家：NVIDIA Shield TV Pro </h2><p><core-commerce id="48781868245d4db7af0fbea452ca9607" data-type="product-list"></core-commerce></p><p>对于那些想要一款可以流式传输电影、运行 PLEX 媒体服务器和玩游戏的一体化设备的用户，可以考虑<a data-i13n="cpos:15;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAfrLWj2eRKubnCxOJ6koR9V2e_xOpmpPHy1pmieoTjyK&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fgp%2Fproduct%2FB07YP9FBMM%2F">NVIDIA 的 Shield TV Pro</a> 。它目前运行 Android TV，目前有点过时，但未来有可能升级到 Google TV。</p><p>凭借功能强大的 Tegra X1+ 处理器，NVIDIA Shield TV Pro 可以以原生 4K 格式进行流传输，还可以通过该公司的 AI 神经网络将 720p 和 1080p 视频升级为 4K。它还支持杜比视界和 HDR10，拥有 3GB RAM、16GB 存储空间和两个 USB-C 端口。此外，还有一个千兆以太网端口、一个 HDMI 插座和一个 microSD 卡插槽。由于它在 Android 上运行，因此您可以使用它来玩 Google Play 商店中的大多数游戏。</p><p>您选择 NVIDIA Shield TV Pro 而不是其他机器的主要原因是它可以让您访问 NVIDIA 的 GeForce Now 云游戏服务。只要您有相对较快的互联网连接，您就可以玩在线传输到 Shield TV Pro 的顶级 PC 游戏。</p><h2>最佳流媒体游戏机：Xbox Series X </h2><p><core-commerce id="87cd14ca853c4dde9b66d45d15edf74f" data-type="product-list"></core-commerce></p><p>尽管索尼的 PlayStation 5 和<a data-i13n="cpos:16;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:;elmt:" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsImxhbmRpbmdVcmwiOiJodHRwczovL3d3dy54Ym94LmNvbS9lbi1VUy9jb25zb2xlcy94Ym94LXNlcmllcy14Pz8iLCJjb250ZW50VXVpZCI6ImI1NTdmMTBhLWE4MzctNDBiMy1hYWE2LTRhZTc3YzJmOTAzOSJ9&amp;signature=AQAAAYWFBZh8fKQ3jrdMV7viiNp1uimN_rtPiqclONMKpFfX&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.xbox.com%2Fen-US%2Fconsoles%2Fxbox-series-x%3F%3F">Xbox Series X</a>都可以传输视频，但我们认为 Xbox 是最适合这项工作的游戏机。它可以播放 4K 蓝光，并支持所有常见的流媒体视频应用程序，包括 Apple TV+ 和 Disney+。然而，PS5 无法以 4K 或杜比全景声传输 Disney+，如果你想观看<em>《曼达洛人》</em>的所有电影辉煌，这会令人失望。</p><p>幸运的是，Xbox Series X 的情况并非如此。最重要的是，Xbox Series X（和 S）还支持杜比视界（Dolby Vision）流媒体视频，这对于拥有较新电视的用户来说尤其有用。当然，Xbox也是一款非常出色的游戏机，它可以访问Game Pass，这是微软的订阅服务，拥有大量的游戏库。</p><p></p>本文最初发表在 Engadget 上：https://www.engadget.com/best-streaming-devices-media-players-123021395.html?src=rss]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/best-streaming-devices-media-players-123021395.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> b557f10a-a837-40b3-aaa6-4ae77c2f9039</guid><dc:creator>妮可·李</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>恩杰特</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder>恩杰特</dc:rightsholder><pubDate>Tue, 05 Sep 2023 16:50:07 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1693932608</ingested><modified> 2023-09-05T16:50:20+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[Technology & Electronics]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Nicole Lee]]></category><media:content height="4000" medium="image" url="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2021-05/1c0b6cc0-bfc7-11eb-b76e-0e9562ca15da" width="6000"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[ ]]></media:title></media:content><media:content height="4000" medium="image" url="https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2021-05/1c0b6cc0-bfc7-11eb-b76e-0e9562ca15da" width="6000"><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[2]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[Kateryna Kukota via Getty Images]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[leisure at home. Watch TV. Remote control in hand close-up.]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[leisure at home. Watch TV. Remote control in hand close-up]]></media:title></media:content></item><item><title><![CDATA[Star Wars Jedi: Survivor patch promises 'solid 60 fps' performance on consoles]]></title><description type="html"><![CDATA[<p> Respawn 和 EA 正在推出<em>《星球大战：绝地幸存者》</em>的重要补丁。该游戏在发布时就受到性能问题的困扰，现在在控制台的性能模式下支持“稳定的 60 fps”。此外，PC 版本（ <a data-i13n="cpos:1;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/star-wars-jedi-survivor-and-the-year-of-disappointing-pc-ports-141551209.html">首当其冲地受到</a>许多性能投诉）也在补丁 7 中获得了一些稳定性改进。</p><p>该游戏的<a data-i13n="cpos:2;pos:1" href="https://www.ea.com/games/starwars/jedi/jedi-survivor/patch-notes">补丁说明</a>称，PS5 和 Xbox Series X/S 用户可以期待“完全重新设计”的性能模式，以获得“大幅”改进的体验。变更日志称，补丁 7 在性能模式下禁用光线追踪，同时提供多项 GPU/CPU 优化以实现“稳定”的 60 fps。开发人员还通过“优化”改进了质量模式（优先考虑图形保真度而不是一致的帧速率），以帮助减少帧速率波动并改善视觉效果。</p><span id="end-legacy-contents"></span><p>尽管第七个补丁的亮点是针对主机用户的，但 PC 用户也不会被蒙在鼓里。 Respawn 为游戏的 Windows 版本添加了对<a data-i13n="cpos:3;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/nvidias-dlss-35-makes-ray-traced-games-look-better-with-ai-130012143.html">Nvidia DLSS（深度学习超级采样）</a>的支持。此外，PC 用户应该会看到“额外的性能和优化改进”。 </p><figure><img src="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-09/93f0a340-4c06-11ee-aefb-a420a17d2a4b" data-crop-orig-src="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-09/93f0a340-4c06-11ee-aefb-a420a17d2a4b" style="height:818px;width:1454px;" alt="游戏“星球大战：绝地幸存者”的媒体资产，展示了主角（卡尔·凯斯蒂斯）站在一片广阔的风景前，这里有突出的悬崖和古老的建筑。从英雄背后看。" data-uuid="29235e57-7bcc-3dc8-8cbe-575ca72f8b11"><figcaption></figcaption><div class="photo-credit">重生 / EA</div></figure><p> PS5版<em>《绝地求生者》</em>也首次获得可变刷新率支持。索尼四月份<a data-i13n="cpos:4;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/ps5-variable-refresh-rate-vrr-release-date-193228613.html">在其最新游戏机中添加了</a>该功能，可动态地将电视或显示器的刷新率与 PS5 的刷新率相匹配，从而减少屏幕撕裂等视觉伪影。索尼表示，它可以帮助更快地渲染场景并减少输入延迟。</p><p>该补丁的亮点包括修复损坏的游戏保存文件的调整以及玩家在“某些情况下”死亡后无法收集 XP 的问题。 Respawn 还承诺在所有平台上进行各种崩溃/错误修复和其他改进。</p><p> <em>《星球大战：绝地幸存者》</em>可在 PS5、Xbox Series X/S 和 Windows 上玩。 PS4 和 Xbox One 端口正在<a data-i13n="cpos:5;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/star-wars-jedi-survivor-will-be-ported-to-ps4-and-xbox-one-after-all-064100551.html">开发中</a>，但尚未确定发布日期。</p>本文最初发表在 Engadget 上：https://www.engadget.com/star-wars-jedi-survivor-patch-promises-solid-60-fps-performance-on-consoles-162223095.html?src=rss]] >; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/star-wars-jedi-survivor-patch-promises-solid-60-fps-performance-on-consoles-162223095.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> af5142c1-1d1b-45f3-8621-5d9d71098da2</guid><dc:creator>威尔·尚克林</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>恩杰特</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder>恩杰特</dc:rightsholder><pubDate>Tue, 05 Sep 2023 16:22:23 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1693930651</ingested><modified> 2023-09-05T16:17:36+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[Information Technology]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Will Shanklin]]></category><media:content height="818" medium="image" url="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-09/4a5cb080-4c05-11ee-bdcf-6221a1945d91" width="1454"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[ ]]></media:title></media:content><media:content height="818" medium="image" url="https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-09/4a5cb080-4c05-11ee-bdcf-6221a1945d91" width="1454"><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[2]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[Respawn / EA]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[Media asset from 'Star Wars: Jedi Survivor.' The protagonist, Cal Kestis, stands facing the "camera" with his droid (BD-1) strapped to his back.]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[Jedi Survivor]]></media:title></media:content></item><item><title><![CDATA[The best Chromebooks you can buy in 2023]]></title><description type="html"><![CDATA[<p>鉴于当今市场上的型号繁多，根据您的需求和预算选择最好的 Chromebook 可能很困难。多年的软件更新以及笔记本电脑制造商制造出功能更强大、制造更精良、电池寿命更长的笔记本电脑，这意味着有大量的 Chrome OS 机器可以作为日常驾驶使用。但在选择 Chromebook 之前，您应该牢记一些特殊因素。从 Lenovo IdeaPad Flex 5i 到 Acer Chromebook Spin 714，我们的首选将帮助您确定哪款 Chromebook 值得您购买。</p><h2>什么是 Chrome 操作系统？为什么我要在 Windows 上使用它？</h2><p>这可能是有关 Chromebook 的第一个问题。市场上有很多廉价的 Windows 笔记本电脑，那么为什么还要费心使用 Chrome 操作系统呢？很高兴你问了。对我来说，Chrome 操作系统的简单和干净的本质是一个很大的卖点。 Chrome 操作系统基于 Google 的 Chrome 浏览器，这意味着您可以运行的大多数程序都是基于网络的。没有像 Windows 笔记本电脑上常见的那样需要卸载臃肿软件或不需要的应用程序，它可以在几秒钟内启动，并且您几乎可以同样快地完全重置为出厂设置。</p><span id="end-legacy-contents"></span><p>当然，对于某些用户来说，简单性也是一个主要缺点。如果您是视频编辑器或软件开发人员，则无法安装本机软件可能会成为问题。但也有很多人在网络浏览器中完成大部分工作。但谷歌及其软件合作伙伴在支持更高级功能方面每年都在进步。例如，Google 在 Chromebook 上的 Google Photos 应用程序中<a data-i13n="cpos:1;pos:1" href="https://support.google.com/photos/thread/208682996/bring-your-creativity-to-life-with-photos%E2%80%99-new-video-editing-features-on-chromebook?hl=en">添加了视频编辑工具</a>- 它不会取代 Adob​​e Premiere，但对很多人来说应该很方便。</p><p>谷歌还增加了对 Chromebook 上 Android 应用程序的支持，这极大地扩展了可用软件的数量。质量差异很大，但这意味着您可以使用 Chromebook 做更多事情，而不仅仅是基于网络的应用程序。例如，您可以安装 Netflix 应用程序并保存视频以供离线观看。 Microsoft Office 和 Adob​​e Lightroom 等其他 Android 应用程序的功能也令人惊讶。在 Android 应用程序和网络应用程序的全面改进之间，Chromebook 不仅仅是一个浏览器。</p><h2> Chromebook 的优点是什么？ </h2><figure><img src="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2022-08/38bdd2f0-2488-11ed-affd-31657bb03b0c" alt="三台 Chromebook 笔记本电脑叠放在一起，稍微呈扇形展开，放在木桌上的桌面保护罩上。" data-uuid="24972f7b-1262-3d93-8e2b-f189a92fda1b"><figcaption></figcaption><div class="photo-credit">内森·英格拉汉姆 / Engadget</div></figure><p>简而言之，网络浏览和任何基于网络的内容。浏览、流媒体音乐和视频以及使用各种社交媒体网站是人们在 Chromebook 上最常见的日常任务。正如您所料，它们还可以与照片、文档、Gmail、云端硬盘、Keep 等 Google 服务配合良好。是的，任何可以运行 Chrome 的计算机都可以做到这一点，但 Google Chrome 操作系统的轻量级特性使其成为一个响应灵敏且稳定的平台。</p><p>正如我之前提到的，Chrome 操作系统可以运行 Android 应用程序，因此如果您是 Android 用户，您会发现平台之间存在一些良好的联系。您可以在 Chromebook 上获取手机上的大多数相同应用程序，并保持它们之间的信息同步。您还可以使用某些 Android 手机作为 Chromebook 的安全密钥，或立即限制您的笔记本电脑使用移动数据。</p><p>谷歌继续将安全性视为 Chromebook 的主要差异化因素，我认为这绝对是一个值得考虑的因素。第一道防线是自动更新。 Chrome 操作系统更新可在后台快速下载，只需快速重启即可安装最新版本。谷歌表示，Chromebook 上的每个网页和应用程序也都在自己的沙箱中运行，因此任何安全威胁都包含在各个应用程序中。最后，Chrome 操作系统有一个名为“验证启动”的自检功能，每次设备启动时都会运行。 Beyond all this, the simple fact that you generally can&#39;t install traditional apps on a Chromebook means there are a lot fewer ways for bad actors to access the system.</p><p> As for when to avoid them, the answer is simple: If you rely heavily on a specific native application for Windows or a Mac, chances are you won&#39;t find the exact same option on a Chromebook. That&#39;s most true in fields like photo and video editing, but it can also be the case in law or finance. Plenty of businesses run on Google&#39;s G suite software, but more still have specific requirements that a Chromebook might not match. If you&#39;re an iPhone user, you&#39;ll also miss out on the way the iPhone easily integrates with an iPad or Mac. For me, the big downside is not being able to access iMessage on a Chromebook.</p><p> Finally, gaming Chromebooks are not ubiquitous, although they&#39;re becoming a <em>slightly</em> more reasonable option with the rise of cloud gaming. In late 2022, Google and some hardware partners announced a push to make Chromebooks with <a data-i13n="cpos:2;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/google-cloud-gaming-chromebooks-asus-lenovo-acer-130030080.html">cloud gaming</a> in mind. From a hardware perspective, that means laptops with bigger screens that have higher refresh rates as well as optimizing those laptops to work with services like NVIDIA GeForce Now, Xbox Game Pass and Amazon Luna. You&#39;ll obviously need an internet connection to use these services, but the good news is that playing modern games on a Chromebook isn&#39;t impossible. You can install Android games from the Google Play Store, but that&#39;s not what most people are thinking of when they want to game on a laptop.</p><p> There&#39;s another potential change on the horizon, as Valve and Google are working to bring the massive Steam catalog to Chromebooks. Right now, Steam is only available as an early alpha on a handful of devices with higher specs, but it works a lot better than I expected. Of course, you&#39;re still not going to run the most demanding games on basic laptops, but the Steam catalog is so vast that there are plenty of titles that worked on the Chromebook I tested it with. Hopefully, Steam will be supported on more devices soon, <a data-i13n="cpos:3;pos:1" href="https://www.chromium.org/chromium-os/steam-on-chromeos/">but the list</a> is somewhat limited at the moment.</p><h2> What are the most important specs for a Chromebook? </h2><figure><img src="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2021-06/28c4bed0-cd37-11eb-a7ff-de290c52cdf7" alt="Acer Chromebook Spin 713" data-uuid="fc221c8a-c134-348a-a3e8-03c468c702c4"><figcaption></figcaption><div class="photo-credit"> Nathan Ingraham / Engadget</div></figure><p> Chrome OS is lightweight and usually runs well on fairly modest hardware, so the most important thing to look for might not be processor power or storage space. That said, I&#39;d still recommend you get a Chromebook with a relatively recent Intel processor, ideally a 10th-gen or newer Intel i3. Most non-Intel Chromebooks I&#39;ve tried haven&#39;t had terribly strong performance, but that&#39;s starting to change – as we evaluate more of these Chromebooks, we&#39;ll recommend ones that have enough power to be good everyday computers.</p><p> As for RAM, 8GB should be the target, unless you&#39;re looking for a budget model and know that your needs are fairly modest. Storage space is another place where you don&#39;t need to spend too much; 64GB should be fine for almost anyone. If you plan on storing a lot of files locally or loading up your Chromebook with Linux or Android apps, get 128GB. But for what it&#39;s worth, I&#39;ve never felt like I might run out of storage when using Chrome OS.</p><p> Things like the keyboard and display quality are arguably more important than sheer specs. The good news is that you can find less expensive Chromebooks that still have pretty good screens and keyboards that you won&#39;t mind typing on all day. Many cheap Chromebooks still come with tiny, low-resolution displays, but at this point there&#39;s no reason to settle for anything less than 1080p. (If you&#39;re looking for an extremely portable, 11-inch Chromebook, though, you&#39;ll probably end up with a lesser screen.) Obviously, keyboard quality is a bit more subjective, but there are plenty of affordable options that offer strong typing experiences.</p><p> Google has an Auto Update policy for Chromebooks, and while that&#39;s not a spec, per se, it&#39;s worth checking before you buy. Basically, Chromebooks get regular software updates automatically for about six years from their release date (though that can vary from device to device). <a data-i13n="cpos:4;pos:1" href="https://support.google.com/chrome/a/answer/6220366?hl=en">This support page</a> lists the Auto Update expiration date for virtually every Chromebook ever, but a good rule of thumb is to buy the newest machine you can to maximize your support.</p><h2> How much should I spend?</h2><p> Chromebooks started out notoriously cheap, with list prices often coming in under $300. But as they&#39;ve gone more mainstream, they&#39;ve transitioned from being essentially modern netbooks to the kind of laptop you&#39;ll want to use all day. As such, prices have increased a bit over the last few years. At this point, you should expect to spend at least $400 if you want a solid daily driver. There are still many budget options out there that may be suitable as secondary devices, but Chromebooks that can be an all-day, every-day laptop will cost a bit more.</p><p> There are also plenty of premium Chromebooks that approach or even exceed $1,000, but I don&#39;t recommend spending that much. Generally, that&#39;ll get you a better design with more premium materials, as well as more powerful internals and extra storage space. Of course, you also sometimes pay for the brand name. But, the specs I outlined earlier are usually enough. That said, if money is no object, there are a few really fabulous options out there.</p><p> <strong>See Also:</strong></p><ul><li><p> <a data-i13n="cpos:5;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/best-laptops-120008636.html"><strong>Best Laptops for 2023</strong></a></p></li><li><p> <a data-i13n="cpos:6;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/best-gaming-laptops-172033838.html"><strong>Best Gaming Laptops</strong></a></p></li><li><p> <a data-i13n="cpos:7;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/best-2-in-1-laptops-173038508.html"><strong>Best 2-in-1 Laptops for 2023</strong></a></p></li><li><p> <a data-i13n="cpos:8;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/best-affordable-windows-laptops-123000512.html"><strong>Best Cheap Windows Laptops</strong></a></p></li><li><p> <a data-i13n="cpos:9;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/best-laptops-for-students-130054631.html"><strong>Best Laptops for College Students</strong></a></p></li></ul><h2> Best bang for your buck: Lenovo IdeaPad Flex 5i</h2><p><core-commerce id="c041afb984ff410098fa7151948cc5b7" data-type="product-list"></p><p> Lenovo has been making some of the best affordable Chromebooks you can buy for several years now, and the <a data-i13n="cpos:10;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAWR6WZjttzosh6Ce0d6Fpj3kauddLu2r8ficQD_ifAjY&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FLenovo-2-1-Chromebook-Computer%2Fdp%2FB09RNCN3YV%3Fth%3D1">IdeaPad Flex 5i</a> is an affordable laptop that provides just about everything you could want in a basic Chromebook. The 13.3-inch, 1080p touchscreen is extremely bright and fairly sharp; I wish it had a taller aspect ratio than 16:9, but it&#39;s pretty common in Chromebooks. This Lenovo Chromebook runs on a 11th-generation Intel Core i3 processor and includes 8GB of RAM and 128GB of storage. While the processor is starting to show its age, it should still be sufficient for most tasks. Eight hours of battery life is pretty good for a laptop in this price range, and the backlit keyboard is excellent for such an affordable device. The key caps feel a little small under my fingers, but that&#39;s the only real complaint I have.</p><p> Other things in the Flex 5i&#39;s favor include that it has both USB-C and USB-A ports, a microSD card slot and a security lock. At three pounds and 0.66 inches thick, it&#39;s not the lightest or slimmest option out there, but it&#39;s totally reasonable considering the price. Finally, the Flex 5i will receive software and security updates until June of 2029, so you can buy this computer and have it covered for years to come.</p><p> Ultimately, the Ideapad Flex 5i hits the sweet spot for a lot of Chromebook buyers out there, providing a level of quality and performance that&#39;s pretty rare to find at this price point. That said, given this laptop has been out for over a year now, we&#39;re keeping an eye out for a replacement from Lenovo, as well as comparable options other manufacturers release.</p><p> The Lenovo Flex 5i is no longer available directly from Lenovo, but you can commonly find it on Amazon for about $400 (as of this writing, it is selling for $368). That&#39;s an outstanding value.</p><h2> Upgrade option: Acer Chromebook Spin 714</h2><p><core-commerce id="95f0b0e58f474f4d9f29d13316b97c4b" data-type="product-list"></p><p></p><p><a data-i13n="cpos:11;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAX1QeRQ01eSgnQlMtotxLWXdsieMp9lLHwOn72xLOT_S&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FAcer-Chromebook-2-Touchscreen-Built%2Fdp%2FB0BJH9LGK8">Acer&#39;s Chromebook Spin 714</a> has long been one of the best premium Chromebook options out there, and this year&#39;s update is no exception. It&#39;s a modest tweak to the 2022 model, but given how good that computer is I have no issues recommending the latest edition. We haven&#39;t tested it yet, but Acer will have a review model for us soon.</p><p> The Spin 714 features a 14-inch, 1900x1200 touchscreen. That works out to a taller 16:10 aspect ratio than you&#39;ll get from the 1080p panels on most Chromebooks. I&#39;m a big fan of taller laptop screens, and while this isn&#39;t as luxurious as the few 3:2 ratio Chromebooks on the market, it&#39;s still a comfortable and high quality screen.</p><p> One noteworthy new feature is the 2K webcam included in the Spin 714. In a world where we&#39;re all doing more video calls than we&#39;d like, having a camera that doesn&#39;t reduce you to a blurry spot is definitely appreciated.</p><p> As for the rest of the hardware, the 13th-generation Intel Core i5 processor should be more than enough power for most tasks, and the keyboard and trackpad on the 2022 model are solid, if not the best. The same can be said for battery life: I got about seven hours using the Spin 714 in my normal daily routine. That&#39;s not exceptional, but it&#39;s in line with what I&#39;ve seen on other i5-powered Chromebooks. Rounding out the hardware is 8GB of RAM and a generous 256GB of storage space. The latest Spin 714 model isn&#39;t listed on Google&#39;s support page, but last year&#39;s model is supported until June 2030; the latest model&#39;s window should run through June of 2031.</p><p> Another bonus is that its hardware meets Google&#39;s recommended specs to run Steam, so gamers might want to give it a shot and see what games they can install.</p><p> Just as the name suggests, the Spin 714 has a 360-degree hinge which lets you use the laptop in tablet mode. I&#39;m not a fan of this convertible design – I don&#39;t know who wants to use a 3-plus pound tablet, but Acer did include a built-in stylus for handwriting notes or drawing in apps like the built-in Chrome Canvas.</p><p> The latest Spin 714 costs $700 – not an unreasonable price for a computer with these specs and built quality. For most people, the Lenovo model will be enough. But, if you&#39;re a serious multitasker, want a better display and keyboard, or just want a computer that&#39;ll last as long as possible, the Acer Spin 714 is easy to recommend. We&#39;ll update this guide once we receive our test model from Acer so we can give updated impressions, particularly on battery life.</p><h2> A good large-screen option: Acer Chromebook 516 GE</h2><p><core-commerce id="71a3b213e2744dcbbd780b3abc02d825" data-type="product-list"></p><p> Acer introduced the <a data-i13n="cpos:12;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiI2NmVhNTY3YS1jOTg3LTRjMmUtYTJmZi0wMjkwNGVmZGU2ZWEiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYW1hem9uLmNvbS9BY2VyLUNocm9tZWJvb2stNTE2LUdFLWk1LTEyNDBQL2RwL0IwQlZWVEwzODg_dGg9MSZ0YWc9Z2RndDBjLXAtby0zci0yMCIsImNvbnRlbnRVdWlkIjoiNzFjYTM1NWUtYmUwNi0zYmEyLWE4NGEtM2U1NWExOWRiYzg0In0&amp;signature=AQAAAeMPwDw6u8YHqYCk03cgZETQzsbwwkoyPvHFf1lC0Mi_&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FAcer-Chromebook-516-GE-i5-1240P%2Fdp%2FB0BVVTL388%3Fth%3D1">Chromebook 516 GE</a> in the fall of 2022 as part of Google&#39;s push to make devices suitable for cloud gaming, but you don&#39;t need to be a gamer <a data-i13n="cpos:13;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/acer-chromebook-516-ge-hands-on-preview-170011142.html">to appreciate this laptop</a> . For $650, you&#39;ll get a 16-inch display with a 2,560 x 1,600 resolution and a 120hz refresh rate. NVIDIA&#39;s GeForce now gaming service supports up to 4K visuals at 120hz on its Ultimate tier so you&#39;ll get to see those benefits. This laptop also supports Steam, yet another reason gamers might be interested in trying it. But even non-gamers should enjoy the 516 GE&#39;s crisp and clear screen and refined hardware.</p><p> It also includes Intel&#39;s 12th-gen Core i7 1240P processor, 8GB of RAM and 256 GB of storage. Given the laptop&#39;s size, it&#39;s good that Acer didn&#39;t skimp on ports here: there&#39;s an HDMI port, USB-C, USB-A, ethernet and a headphone jack. The keyboard has gamer-friendly LED lights that you can customize, but more importantly it&#39;s just a solid and comfortable keyboard, whether you&#39;re playing games or just typing up reports. The trackpad is large and responsive, as well.</p><p> The 516 GE only weighs 3.75 pounds too – pretty light for a laptop with a 16-inch screen. Between the powerful hardware, solid design, good trackpad and keyboard and great screen, anyone who wants a bigger Chromebook will likely be happy with this model. As for support, Google says the 516 GE will continue receiving updates until June of 2030.</p><h2> Honorable mention: HP Dragonfly Pro Chromebook</h2><p><core-commerce id="d51234aaaa91453e94b11f10e2170144" data-type="product-list"></p><p> If you just want the nicest Chromebook you can buy, with top-shelf specs and design, the $999 <a data-i13n="cpos:14;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:HP Store;elmt:;" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=8a0e8870-4cf8-4bda-935c-af7c00c28e2b&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=HP+Store&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAATmD35Ks726xdz2LVY7LDZXAS0u_pQiizwieyaJc96qW&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hp.com%2Fus-en%2Fshop%2Fpdp%2Fhp-dragonfly-pro-chromebook-16gb-bk">HP Dragonfly Pro Chromebook</a> might meet your needs. For starters, the screen is an absolute stand out. It&#39;s a 14-inch, 2,560 x 1,600 touchscreen that maxes out at an extremely bright 1,200 nits.</p><p> The keyboard and trackpad, meanwhile, are probably the best I&#39;ve tested lately. The keyboard has an extremely satisfying clickiness when you&#39;re typing. It&#39;s no mechanical keyboard, but it felt reassuringly solid and there was no real adjustment period needed when I started banging away on this laptop. The large trackpad is excellent, with great responsiveness and a solid click. There&#39;s also a fingerprint reader so you can unlock the laptop without a password, another premium feature that I wish I saw in more Chromebooks.</p><p> From a specs perspective, the Dragonfly Pro includes a 12th-gen Core i5 i5-1235U processor – not the absolute latest, but plenty of power nonetheless. That&#39;s matched with 16GB of RAM and 256GB of storage, and I definitely noticed the extra RAM makes a difference in responsiveness across the board.</p><p> Other niceties include an 8-megapixel webcam, a shooter that exceeds what you&#39;ll find on most laptops, whether they&#39;re in this price range or not. HP did this without resorting to a huge bezel, either – the top bezel is thicker than the ones on the side, but not so much that the laptop feels unbalanced. And the Bang &amp; Olufsen quad speaker setup is shockingly good. With volume set to about 33 percent, the laptop was plenty loud to fill my office, and it was also fairly well balanced, with prominent bass, surprising stereo separation and clear highs. These are definitely some of the best laptop speakers I&#39;ve ever heard.</p><p> That said, there is a major caveat here. The HP Dragonfly Pro&#39;s battery life is poor — under 5 hours poor, which is very disappointing for a $999 laptop. It&#39;s bad enough that I went back and forth on recommending this device. People who don&#39;t travel a lot and do most of their work at their desk might not care, but in that case, why bother getting one of the thinnest and lightest Chromebooks out there?</p><p> The other downside is that you don&#39;t get a variety of ports here – just four USB-C, and no headphone jack. That&#39;s not a total dealbreaker, as I don&#39;t often find myself plugging much into my Chromebooks, but again it&#39;s definitely worth knowing.</p><p> This laptop is otherwise a total delight to use, as it is extremely well built, powerful and features a great keyboard and screen. I definitely wouldn&#39;t recommend it to everyone with these battery issues, but if you want one of the nicest Chromebooks you can buy and don&#39;t spend a ton of time away from a charger (and have plenty of disposable income), you&#39;ll probably enjoy the Dragonfly Pro.</p> This article originally appeared on Engadget at https://www.engadget.com/best-chromebooks-160054646.html?src=rss]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/best-chromebooks-160054646.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> 71ca355e-be06-3ba2-a84a-3e55a19dbc84</guid><dc:creator> Nathan Ingraham</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>恩杰特</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder>恩杰特</dc:rightsholder><pubDate>Tue, 05 Sep 2023 16:22:05 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1693930925</ingested><modified> 2